  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Chakra, Level 4+ </p><p>You've learned to efficiently create constructs of chakra, maximizing their potential for less.</p><p> You gain the following benefits: </p><p>• Increase your Intelligence or Charisma score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• When you are concentrating on a jutsu with the Construct keyword, the first time you would make a concentration check as the result of damage per round, you automatically succeed the check.</p><p>• When you cast a jutsu with the Construct keyword, you may apply two of the following benefits.</p><p> You cannot select the same benefit more than once.</p><p> - Damage rolls from these constructs pierce any passive DR a target possesses.</p><p> - These constructs increase their attack rolls by +1, and impose a -1 penalty to saving throws they impose.</p><p> - These constructs gain an amount of DR against all damage equal to your jutsu casting modifier.</p><p> - These constructs increase their AC by half your jutsu casting modifier.</p><p></p>",
